description: Melissa Lauren is super tough, super cute, and super French, with an accent to die for! She has been doing SM in her private life for a while, but this is her first time playing with water. I give her the full treatment with caning, ice, crotch ropes, and a difficult inverted suspension. In the end she said she loved it all, and I said she could come back anytime! I think you’ll agree.
title: Melissa Lauren
